Class IntDoublyLinkedList

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uprb.datastructure.IntDoublyLinkedList

  • public class IntDoublyLinkedList
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a doubly linked list of integers.

      private class  IntDoublyLinkedList.Node
      Represents a doubly linked list node, which is almost the same as a singly linked list node, but differs in that it contains a reference to the previous node.
